    "Revenue Booked": [9124123, 581877, 0, 986473, 348371, 102375, 1100000, 1100000, 1100000, 1100000, 1100000, 1100000],
    "Gross Margin Booked": [1681090, 120962, 0, 141704, 76083, 28000, 330000, 330000, 330000, 330000, 330000, 330000],
}

df_summary = pd.DataFrame(data)

# Formatting numbers for better readability
df_summary["Revenue Booked"] = df_summary["Revenue Booked"].apply(lambda x: f"${x:,.0f}")
df_summary["Gross Margin Booked"] = df_summary["Gross Margin Booked"].apply(lambda x: f"${x:,.0f}")
df_summary["kW Booked"] = df_summary["kW Booked"].apply(lambda x: f"{x:,}")

import ace_tools as tools; tools.display_dataframe_to_user(name="Forecast Summary for Commercial Sales", dataframe=df_summary)
